
ORDER OF PAYOFF(logic):
1.) Anything over 20%
2.) 15-20% if balance is below $3000
3.) if payment is greater than 5% of balance
4.) by balance
if(accountInterest > 20%)

SITE FEATURES:
1.) Tell you what to pay
2.) Payoff charts, show dates
3.) Keep them motivated

NEEDS:
1.) Easy to use
2.) Quick to sign up
3.) Creative reminders and encouragement

HOMEPAGE:
- Paneled site with details on who we are and why
- Link to sign up or go to account (a transition lightbox to middle of page)

SIGNUP PROCESS:
- Small screen pages with light colored background.
	1.) Name, email, username, password
	2.) Add accounts, click to add new account
		- separate page for each new account
	3.) Budget page for all expenses
	4.) Review page to confirm and suggest any possible ones people forget
	5.) Success page then take to user dashboard

USER DASHBOARD:
-Payoff tables
-Payment dates and amounts
-Edit settings
-Edit accounts
-Monthly budget


FUTURE IDEAS:
- API to accounts
- Mobile app integration

DATABASE:
- Users
- Accounts
- userAccounts
